{{sectionHeading "Helpers and Template Engines"}}

<p>
    Most web applications these days are rendered by a template engine. This project contains helpers for <a href="http://handlebarsjs.com">Handlebars</a> and <a href="http://linkedin.github.io/dustjs/">Dust</a> template engines, as well as <a href="http://reactjs.org">React</a>, a front-end UI library.
</p>

<p>
    These Intl helpers allow you to localize strings without having to interact with the JavaScript API directly. Before using them however, you should have a good understanding on the syntax of your template engine of choice.
</p>

